data.title: Foreign Minister al-Jaafari Delivers Remarks at the Pledging Conference in Support of Iraq
data.meta_description: Iraq Foreign Minister Ibrahim al-Jaafari delivers remarks at the Pledging Conference in Support of Iraq at the U.S. Department of State in Washington, D.C. on July 20, 2016. [State Department Photo/Public Domain]
